<h2 id="Example">  Example  </h2>
<p></p>

The two figures illustrate an exemplary geometry meshed by a regular grid of (hexahedral) elements before (Figure <a href="#fig:originalAndServoLinked">1</a> (a) ) and after the automatic application of periodic boundary conditions (Figure <a href="#fig:originalAndServoLinked">1</a> (b) ).
<p></p>

<div style="clear:both; width:100%; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background:#f4fcf4;">
