			<td class="foswikiTableCol1 foswikiLastCol foswikiLast" style="text-align:center"> <img src="/pub/Documentation/MentatPBCOnBoxMesh/pbcOnBoxMesh_after.png" alt="after servo linking" width='100%' /><br /> (b) Same mesh after automatic application of periodic boundary conditions through servo links (black lines). </td>
		</tr>
	</tbody></table>
